@@TJvShutdownDlg.Execute
Description:
Call this method to display the dialog. if the user clicks the ok button, the system will automatically reboot the way you want.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvShutdownDlg.Reason
Description:
This property is the reason of rebooting. This reason is shown as the first line of the dialog. This property may be blank if you don't want to give any specific reason.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvShutdownDlg.RestartType
Description:
This property is the type of reboot you want (Logoff, shutdown, reboot, restart, ...).

